snippet.title: Naruto Shippuden: Ultimate Ninja Storm Generations Trailer
snippet.description: Check out this trailer for Naruto Shippuden: Ultimate Ninja Storm Generations, showcasing the incredibly cinematic in-game graphics and highlights a few of the 70+ playable characters in the game.
